name: Before Us: A Homestuck Fanzine
description:
“Before Us” is a Homestuck Fanzine that was released October 26, 2018: It's centered around the dancestors, otherwise known as the Alpha Trolls!

This zine features 52 lovely artists who have contributed 50+ pieces of Illustrations and/or Fanfiction for our favorite tertiary group of characters.

Be mindful that some pieces may be jarringly bigger than others due to some artists working on larger canvas sizes.

Have fun peeking through!
